nvasion of Iraq. He then invaded Georgia mere months after Bush opened NATO=
=E2=80=99s door to the former Soviet republic. Putin sent troops into Ukrai=
ne on Obama=E2=80=99s watch in 2014 and worked to ensure his secretary of s=
tate, <strong>Hillary Clinton</strong>, lost the White House two years
later. (Putin <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVD=
